cs.NI, cs.RO, cs.SY, cs.IT, cs.AI 

This paper focuses on the optimization of wireless communication with rotary-wing UAVs, which involves networked systems (cs.NI) and robotics (cs.RO). The problem formulation and solution methods also involve control theory and optimization (cs.SY), information theory (cs.IT), and artificial intelligence (cs.AI).
